OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,FDog owners on the Isle of Wight are
OL,7,Fbeing urged to be vigilant after rat
OL,8,Fpoison was found in a popular walking
OL,9,Fspot.
OL,11,FPolice said they have received a
OL,12,Fnumber of reports this year of dogs
OL,13,Ffalling ill after eating the
OL,14,Fsubstance, which has been scattered
OL,15,Faround Parkhurst Forest.
OL,17,FOfficers have been patrolling the area
OL,18,Fand investigating.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
