PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,FMark Robinson and his daughter's dogs
OL,7,Fhad to be taken to the vets after
OL,8,Feating the substance - he told ITV
OL,9,FMeridian: "I end up with two dogs that
OL,10,Fhave taken some kind of substance, the
OL,11,Flikes of which I don't know what it is.
OL,13,F"But I'm absolutely sure it's not
OL,14,Fnatural and at that point we decide to
OL,15,Ftake them to the vets, pick up some
OL,16,Fexamples to take with me, snd he
OL,17,Fconfirms that it's rat poison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"It's an anticoagulant and both dogs
OL,7,Fthen have to have the injections in
OL,8,Forder to get them to vomit up
OL,9,Feverything.
OL,11,F"Cody really didn't react well to
OL,12,Fthat, the other dog seemed to just
OL,13,Ftake it all in his stride, and #500
OL,14,Flater and a fairly distressing half an
OL,15,Fhour for my dog, at least we know he's
OL,16,Fsafe and sound.Y
OL,18,FMr Robinson says he's not prepared to
OL,19,Favoid the area despite what's happened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,FI've told as many people as I can and
OL,7,Fthere's lots of sort of interaction
OL,8,Famongst the dog community so people
OL,9,Fgenerally know," he added.
OL,11,F"It pains me that whoever is doing
OL,12,Fthis for whatever particular twisted
OL,13,Freason they have shouldn't win so I'm
OL,14,Fnot going to stop using it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"I'm going to be a lot more careful
OL,7,Fand I just sincerely hope that if
OL,8,Fsomebody who has got enough
OL,9,Finformation to help the police
OL,10,Factually get this sorted and get the
OL,11,Findividual sorted that we get a
OL,12,Fresolution to this problem."
OL,14,FMr Robinson's wife Petra said the
OL,15,Fwhole experience left her angry and
OL,16,Fworried.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
