OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"There are lots of stories about dogs
OL,7,Fhaving died as a result of eating the
OL,8,Fpoison and so I thought that could
OL,9,Fhave been him and which clearly would
OL,10,Fbe really distressing.
OL,12,F"He had a rough 24 hours, you know,
OL,13,Fit's the 24 hours afterwards, and he
OL,14,Fcouldn't stand properly, he couldn't
OL,15,Flie down, he was getting up and
OL,16,Fvomiting as well.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"He has a habit of always hanging back
OL,7,Fand we try now to make sure we're
OL,8,Fbehind him all the time so that you've
OL,9,Falways got your eye on him wherever he
OL,10,Fhappens to be.
OL,12,FPolice say they've received reports
OL,13,Ffrom dog walkers from the Marks Corner
OL,14,Fend of the Forest, but this substance
OL,15,Fcould be laid anywhere.
OL,17,FOfficers are contacting local
OL,18,Fstockists of rat poison and have been
OL,19,Fliaising with the Forestry Commission.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,FSergeant Mark Radford of Hampshire
OL,7,FPolice said: "These incidents continue
OL,8,Fto cause concern to people who use the
OL,9,FForest, but most important of all is
OL,10,Fthe harm this is causing to people's
OL,11,Fbeloved pets.
OL,13,F"This is simply unacceptable, and our
OL,14,Fofficers are patrolling the area and
OL,15,Ffollowing up any available lines of
OL,16,Fenquiry.
OL,18,F"If you use the Forest, please be
OL,19,Falert and mindful of your surroundings
OL,20,Fto help keep yourself, your pet and
OL,21,Fothers safe.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"Parkhurst Forest is a vast area, and
OL,7,Fof course is very limited in terms of
OL,8,FCCTV coverage. The deposition of this
OL,9,Fpoison has also been sporadic, so it
OL,10,Fis crucial that members of the public
OL,11,Freport anything they see or find to
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,F"Have you witnessed anyone acting
OL,15,Fsuspiciously in the Forest? Do you
OL,16,Fcycle and use a helmet camera, for
OL,17,Fexample, that may have captured
OL,18,Fsomething?
OL,20,F"Have you found any suspected poison
OL,21,Fin the Forest?
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
