PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777532747
OL,3,CWarning to dog owners after rat poison
OL,4,Cis found at popular walking spot
OL,6,F"Please give us as much detail as you
OL,7,Fcan regarding exactly where and when,
OL,8,Fand any descriptions of suspicious
OL,9,Fpeople you have observed in the area."
